premise_source_doc_sentence: Spectre was filmed from December 2014 to July 2015 , with locations in Austria , the United Kingdom , Italy , Morocco and Mexico .

The film was released on 26 October 2015 in the United Kingdom on the same night as the world premiere at the Royal Albert Hall in London , followed by a worldwide release which included IMAX screenings .
The Spectre R42 is a 2-seater mid-engined rear-wheel drive sportscar built by British speciality car manufacturer Spectre Supersport Ltd. .

Thus , according to Samuel Foster Damon , Spectre epitomizes `` Reason separated from humanity '' and `` Self-centered selfhood '' or , as Alexander S. Gourlay puts it , Spectre is `` characterized by self-defensive rationalization '' .
The Spectre is used by the Swiss armed forces and by Italian special forces , and has been exported elsewhere .
